{"tid":1563414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你會有雨革後期FEEL,全因為香港人軟弱, 唔單止關左膠事, 係關全香港人事","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:59:21.000Z","uid":31637,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ad30d04c8bfa534f81907e275357b04ed6c1c1c1","tid":1563414,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"玉碎抗爭---&gt;手足被打仆街/被打死---&gt;唔敢報仇---&gt;等美國打救<br />\n玉碎抗爭---&gt;手足被打仆街/被打死---&gt;幫手足報仇(行刺/暗殺/掟炸彈)---&gt;自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n姐係你地幾勇武, 都只係敢做玉碎, 唔敢做復仇者, 唔敢做JOKER, 唔敢成立革命黨做革命分子搞革命, 會有雨革後期FEEL真係好撚正常, 都係必定既結局<br />\n<br />\n所以咪撚再弱智係度呻吟, 我一個月前已經睇撚通晒"},{"pid":"192e9abebe959ebb3dbedb38c8f53e6e23a1727c","tid":1563414,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3a389b069481a4ea55b3e40c69a55cbed142a23","tid":1563414,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e5f62ada96d3f5086d806942e8526e7fc46df376","tid":1563414,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"Sad but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fceb37fc88ac43754c14b